OL,3,CCould French-English bilingual schools
OL,4,Cbe introduced to Jersey in 2025?
OL,6,FA Jersey politician has proposed
OL,7,Fintroducing bilingual school tuition
OL,8,Ffrom 2025.
OL,10,FDeputy Sir Philip Bailhache is looking
OL,11,Fto progressively phase in the
OL,12,Fintroduction of French-English
OL,13,Fbilingual lessons in three schools,
OL,14,Fbeginning with reception classes.
OL,16,FHe says the changes would bring
OL,17,Feconomic, political and diplomatic
OL,18,Fadvantages, as well as cultural and
OL,19,Fheritage benefits, given the island's
OL,20,Fhistorical ties to France.
