OL,3,CCould French-English bilingual schools
OL,4,Cbe introduced to Jersey in 2025?
OL,6,FThe proposition will be debated at the
OL,7,Fnext States meeting on Tuesday 10
OL,8,FSeptember.
OL,10,FThe idea of bilingual French-English
OL,11,Fprimary schools has been considered
OL,12,Fsince 2013.
OL,14,FThe Education Department presented a
OL,15,Freport to the Council of Ministers in
OL,16,F2016 which looked at creating one but
OL,17,Fat the time, teachers were not
OL,18,Fconvinced.
