OL,3,CCould French-English bilingual schools
OL,4,Cbe introduced to Jersey in 2025?
OL,6,FFrench lessons are already taught in
OL,7,Fschools but this proposition would see
OL,8,Fthe language integrated in the
OL,9,Fteaching of other subjects so students
OL,10,Fwould spend time learning topics in
OL,11,FEnglish and French.
OL,13,FThe plan suggests that if bilingual
OL,14,Fschools were opened in September 2025,
OL,15,Fit would initially only be open to
OL,16,Fpupils in Reception.
OL,18,FThe following year, bilingual lessons
OL,19,Fwould be delivered to Reception and
OL,20,FYear 1 pupils.
