OL,3,CCould French-English bilingual schools
OL,4,Cbe introduced to Jersey in 2025?
OL,6,FThis staged process means it would
OL,7,Ftake six years for the entire school
OL,8,Fto begin teaching bilingual lessons.
OL,10,FDeputy Bailhache wants to establish
OL,11,Fthree such centres out of the 32 state
OL,12,Fand private primary schools.
OL,14,FA survey conducted with parents in
OL,15,F2016 revealed that at least 60% would
OL,16,Fsend their children to a French
OL,17,Fbilingual school if the option was
OL,18,Favailable.
