OL,3,CCould French-English bilingual schools
OL,4,Cbe introduced to Jersey in 2025?
OL,6,FThe proposal identifies several
OL,7,Fadvantages of French-English learning,
OL,8,Fincluding economic, educational,
OL,9,Fcultural, diplomatic and
OL,10,Fconstitutional.
OL,12,FIt adds that improved communication
OL,13,Fwith France could lead to business
OL,14,Fgrowth.
OL,16,FCulturally, it notes the tuition would
OL,17,Fbenefit life in Jersey as the French
OL,18,Flanguage plays an important part in
OL,19,Fthe island's culture and heritage.
